.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, funk, reggae, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cricket, climbing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##8
5. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | funk         | ambient   | gospel    |
| Sport         | cricket | rugby | climbing | ice-hockey |

