.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, soccer, tennis
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching satire movies##7
2. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching zombie movies##7
4. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
5. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | sports | western | zombie    |
| Sport         | baseball | tennis   | soccer   | lacrosse |

