2. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
6. the person eating eggplant is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
7. the person eating eggplant is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | strawberry | blueberry  | broccoli |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | jazz         | funk | country |

