.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, iced-tea, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing, rugby, baseball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
2. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person who's sport is rugby##7
3. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
4. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
5. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | iced-tea | soy-milk | 7up   |
| Sport      | weightlifting | rugby | baseball  | skiing |

