.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, country, punk, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, bike, van
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of trance and the person driving the quad-bike##2
2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
4. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the fan of punk is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the fan of trance is not to the right of the fan of punk##8
8. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | rock | punk | country |
| Transport     | van | snowmobile       | quad-bike  | bike    |

