3. the person driving the train is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the firefighter is not to the right of the software-developer##8
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | firefighter | software-developer      | scientist   | electrician  |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | subway | train | roller |

