.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, cauliflower, mango, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, baking, collecting
1. the person eating mango is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person eating cauliflower##8
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating mango is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
7. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | cauliflower        | potato | mango      | peas    |
| Hobby   | camping | baking   | gardening | collecting |

