.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking water##7
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | water         | mirinda    | milk       |
| Sport      | climbing | weightlifting | badminton | tennis |

