3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
4. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | cola     | milk | hot-chocolate        | water       |
| Hobby      | baking | rock-climbing  | cooking | writing |

