.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pear, cauliflower, plum
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, horror, satire
 1. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 2. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
 3. the person eating avocado is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
10. the person eating pear is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | pear    | cauliflower | avocado | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | satire  | horror     | mystery    |

