.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, cucumber, potato, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, sudoku, gardening
1. the person eating potato is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating radish##1
5. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person eating cucumber is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating radish##2
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
