.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, pony, mouse, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, skateboard, scooter
1. the owner of the turtle is not the person driving the skateboard##6
2. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the turtle##7
4. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
5. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
7. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | bird  | turtle | pony  | mouse  |
| Transport   | helicopter | train   | scooter | skateboard |

