.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, mouse, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, motorbike, boat
1. the person driving the scooter is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
4. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the tram##1
5. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the tram##7
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | ferret    | pony | goldfish | mouse |
| Transport   | scooter | boat      | motorbike     | tram     |

 